"\r\nThe international project Smart J is a diversified development and additional non-formal education of Jewish children.\">SmartJ</span></a>.\r\n                    Within the frame of this direction, participants gain knowledge on various topics such as: gratitude, Gmilut Hassadim, Tzdaka, prayer,  the clarity of speech, community and much more.<br>\r\n                    The program also provides lessons on Jewish holidays. All the lessons are aimed at the knowledge practical application. They include a large number of games, tasks, interactive exercises. Frequent change of activities allows children not to lose interest in learning.\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-md-6 box\">\r\n                <div class=\"container-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/fa2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <h4 class=\"lain-v\">J-Art – educational direction “science and creativity”</h4>\r\n                <p>The process of developmental education is carried out through project activities. For example, the topics of learning lessons - ecology, sound, floristics. All training is based on <span title=\"S - science, T - technology, E - engineering, A - art, M - mathematics, or: science, technology, engineering, creativity, mathematics. In simple terms,  the disciplines that are becoming the most popular in the modern world. STEAM is one of the  implementation direction of project and teaching -  research activities,  in and out of school.\">STEAM</span>, <span title=\"By giving students to collect LEGO, we motivate their natural curiosity and the desire to create.\r\nStudents comprehend the experience gained, draw conclusions and discuss them with each other and with the teacher. They can demonstrate their projects and present solutions which have been implemented.  \">Lego Education</span> technology using the <span title=\"An interactive Smartboard is a device used together with a projector and a computer. The image from the computer is displayed on the interactive smartboard, like on a simple screen, with the help of a projector. \">Smartboard</span>, thanks to which lessons become more interactive and children memorize material faster, as the learning process  turns into an exciting game.It is important that families are  being together during  learning process, so it is necessary to conduct a one lesson per month in united groups.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-4\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"50\" class=\"parallax bg-5\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-6\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"90\" class=\"parallax bg-8\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"20\" class=\"parallax bg-229\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"40\" class=\"parallax bg-9\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-10\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-11\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-12\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-13\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"50\" class=\"parallax bg-14\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-15\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"40\" class=\"parallax bg-16\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-17\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-18\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-19\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-20\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-09\"></i>\r\n    </section>\r\n    <div class=\"form container-fluid\" id=\"contact\">\r\n        <h5 class=\"text-uppercase text-center\">CONTACT US</h5>\r\n        <form action=\"\" class=\"contact-form pbz_form clear-styles\">\r\n            <div class=\"row text-center\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-lg-4 col-xs-12 col