in learning:</h4>\r\n                    <p>A system of unique, creative, and intellectual development that helps to open up and “unlock  the potential”. Studying process based on <span title=\"S - science, T - technology, E - engineering, A - art, M - mathematics, or: science, technology, engineering, creativity, mathematics. In simple terms,  the disciplines that are becoming the most popular in the modern world. STEAM is one of the  implementation direction of project and teaching -  research activities,  in and out of school.\">STEAM</span> approach</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi b-none\">\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Global<br>\r\n                        Jewish Network:</h4>\r\n                    <p>The feeling of unity of the Jewish people, regardless of the place of living, a sense of belonging to  the global Jewish community.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi b-none b-2\">\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Warm<br>\r\n                        family atmosphere:</h4>\r\n                    <p>A platform where you can discuss topics of interest, learn, develop and feel like at home.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-09\"></i>\r\n    </section> \r\n\r\n    <!--/////////////////-->\r\n    <div class=\"center wrapper-box\">\r\n        <div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi\">\r\n                <div class=\"cont-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/im-box-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Jewish heritage:</h4>\r\n                    <p>Studying the history and traditions of Jewish people.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi\">\r\n                <div class=\"cont-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/im-box-2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Novelty in learning:</h4>\r\n                    <p>A system of unique, creative, and intellectual development that helps to open up and “unlock  the potential”. Studying process based on <span title=\"S - science, T - technology, E - engineering, A - art, M - mathematics, or: science, technology, engineering, creativity, mathematics. In simple terms,  the disciplines that are becoming the most popular in the modern world. STEAM is one of the  implementation direction of project and teaching -  research activities,  in and out of school.\">STEAM</span> approach </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi\">\r\n                <div class=\"cont-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/im-box-3.png.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Global Jewish Network:</h4>\r\n                    <p>The feeling of unity of the Jewish people, regardless of the place of living, a sense of belonging to  the global Jewish community.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div>\r\n            <div class=\"wr-princi\">\r\n                <div class=\"cont-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/im-box-4.png.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"princi-description text-left\">\r\n                    <h4 class=\"lain-v\">Warm family atmosphere:</h4>\r\n                    <p>A platform where you can discuss topics of interest, learn, develop and feel like at home.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!--/////////////////-->\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"join-bg\">\r\n        <div class=\"content text-center row\">\r\n            <h5 class=\"text-uppercase\">PARENTS AND CHILDREN</h5>\r\n            <strong class=\"col-lg-12\">Meetings are held in different formats: for all children\'s groups together with the groups of  parents,  or for one group of children with one group of parents.<br><br> Especially for this purpose, we developed different programs and projects, where family members participate together. This approach helps to find common interests that make parents and children closer.</strong>\r\n            <div class=\"btn-container\">\r\n                <a data-tilt class=\"text-uppercase popup-btn\" data-mfp-src=\"#contact-form-parent\" href=\"#\">Join in</a>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n    <section class=\"container wr-serv\" id=\"education\">\r\n        <div class=\"caption text-center\">\r\n            <h5 class=\"text-uppercase\">HARMONY COMBINATION IN EDUCATION </h5>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"row serv-content\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-6 col-md-6 box\">\r\n                <div class=\"container-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/fa1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <h4 class=\"lain-v\">J-Roots - strengthening ties with the roots of your nation</h4>\r\n                <p>The lesson cycle on values and traditions of the Jewish people, developed in conjunction with\r\n                    an educational project <a href=\"http://www.darkeinu.org\"><span title=\"For the first time ever a complex educational system for teaching Jewish heritage disciplines was created in the Russian language for Jewish schools and kindergartens in countries of the former Soviet Union.\">Darkeinu</span></a> and an international project <a href=\" http://smart-j.org\"><span title=\"\r\nThe international project Smart J is a diversified development and additional non-formal education of Jewish children.\">SmartJ</span></a>.\r\n                    Within the frame of this direction, participants gain knowledge on various topics such as: gratitude, Gmilut Hassadim, Tzdaka, prayer,  the clarity of speech, community and much more.<br>\r\n                    The program also provides lessons on Jewish holidays. All the lessons are aimed at the knowledge practical application. They include a large number of games, tasks, interactive exercises. Frequent change of activities allows children not to lose interest in learning.\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-6 col-md-6 box\">\r\n                <div class=\"container-img\">\r\n                    <img src=\"/wp-content/themes/jfuture/images/fa2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <h4 class=\"lain-v\">J-Art – educational direction “science and creativity”</h4>\r\n                <p>The process of developmental education is carried out through project activities. For example, the topics of learning lessons - ecology, sound, floristics. All training is based on <span title=\"S - science, T - technology, E - engineering, A - art, M - mathematics, or: science, technology, engineering, creativity, mathematics. In simple terms,  the disciplines that are becoming the most popular in the modern world. STEAM is one of the  implementation direction of project and teaching -  research activities,  in and out of school.\" class=\"popup-btn\" data-mfp-src=\"#STEAM\">STEAM</span>, <span title=\"By giving students to collect LEGO, we motivate their natural curiosity and the desire to create.\r\nStudents comprehend the experience gained, draw conclusions and discuss them with each other and with the teacher. They can demonstrate their projects and present solutions which have been implemented.\" class=\"popup-btn\" data-mfp-src=\"#Lego\">Lego Education</span> technology using the <span title=\"An interactive Smartboard is a device used together with a projector and a computer. The image from the computer is displayed on the interactive smartboard, like on a simple screen, with the help of a projector.\" class=\"popup-btn\" data-mfp-src=\"#board\">Smartboard</span>, thanks to which lessons become more interactive and children memorize material faster, as the learning process  turns into an exciting game.It is important that families are  being together during  learning process, so it is necessary to conduct a one lesson per month in united groups.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-4\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"50\" class=\"parallax bg-5\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-6\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"90\" class=\"parallax bg-8\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"20\" class=\"parallax bg-229\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"40\" class=\"parallax bg-9\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-10\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-11\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-12\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-13\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"50\" class=\"parallax bg-14\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"100\" class=\"parallax bg-15\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"40\" class=\"parallax bg-16\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-17\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-18\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-19\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"80\" class=\"parallax bg-20\"></i>\r\n        <i data-offset=\"70\" class=\"parallax bg-09\"></i>\r\n    </sect